data.text: Welcome to Old Mill Village: Where Smart Living Meets Mountain Serenity! Nestled in Heber, Utah, our 3-bed, 2.5-bath residences feature state-of-the-art smart home tech for modern convenience. With Walmart, Heber Valley Hospital, and Wasatch High School less than 2 miles away, enjoy essential amenities while surrounded by outdoor activities and scenic hikes. Discover the perfect balance of accessibility and tranquility at Old Mill Village in Heber, Utah. Unit A: 1,916 Total sqft 1507 sqft Living 409 sqft Garage Unit B: 1,869 Total sqft 1460 sqft Living 409 sqft Garage Upcoming Features at Old Mill Village: Clubhouse Playground Fitness Center RESIDENT LEASE PROGRAMS: $175.00/month Includes the Following: Liability Insurance: Available through MAXX PM, or your own provider Resident Solutions Package (RSP) *Required: Residents receive HVAC filters delivered around every 60 days Online ACH Payments Resident Portal Access Maintenance Portal, and 24/hr. Emergency Maintenance Call Line Smart Home Package: App Controlled Smarthome Smart Home Door Lock Smart Thermostat Smart Water Bugs High-Speed Internet HOA Amenities Access Snow Removal Landscaping *Please note that the units showcased are model units, and individual rental units may have different restrictions and features.*
